{"title":"我愿做一架犁","authors":["张永枚"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":6,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿做一架犁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张永枚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国呵，多辽阔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边无际的好土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国呵，在召唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更多的棉花更多的米！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国呵，听见吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在这样回答你："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我这一个年青人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿做一架铁的犁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我这一架犁呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立下了大志气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁碎拦路石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩断荆和棘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前开劈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁呵！犁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁呵！向前犁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀起黄土的波涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱着红色的歌曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁愿损伤自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不玷污荣誉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永不泄气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远锋利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁呵！向前犁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国呵，你听吧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要犁遍所有的生荒地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让丰收的花果呀香万里！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}